Name: DK_IHE_practiceSettingCode_VS
Title: DK_IHE_practiceSettingCode_VS
Descriptino: Values used for the document metadata attribute practiceSettingCode, which is an attribute specifying the clinical specialty where the act that resulted in the document was performed (e.g., Family Practice, Laboratory, Radiology). The value set is based on a subset of the code list from the SOR lookup table 'SOR-Enhedstyper' (http://sor.sundhedsstyrelsen.dsdn.dk/lookupdata/#EntityTypes, accessable on Sundhedsdatanettet (SDN)), which is based on SNOMED codes.

Name: DK_IHE_TypeCode_VS
Title: DK_IHE_TypeCode_VS
Descriptino: Value set for the typeCode attribute. The typeCode specifies the precise type of document from the user perspective. The granularity of typeCode is finer grained than its superior classCode.

Name: Hl7VSExpandedYesNoIndicator
Title: hl7VS-expandedYes-NoIndicator
Descriptino: Value Set of codes that specify an expansion on the original Yes/No indicator table by including "flavors of null".  It is intended to be applied to fields where the response is not limited to "yes" or "no".
